Pursuant to:
- Circular No. 21/2013/TT-NHNN dated September 09, 2013 of the Governor of the State Bank of Vietnam on promulgating the Regulations on the operational network of commercial banks; 
- Circular No. 01/2022/TT-NHNN dated January 28, 2022 amending and supplementing some articles of Circular No. 21/2013/TT-NHNN dated 09/9/2013 of the Governor of the State Bank of Vietnam on promulgating the Regulations on the operational network of commercial banks;
- Legal Document No. 897/HCM-TTr3 dated April 02, 2024 of the State Bank of Vietnam-Ho Chi Minh City Branch on relocating Binh Thanh Branch;
Asia Commercial Bank is pleased to announce that Binh Thanh Branch shall be relocated due to the change of house number according to the announcement of the People’s Committee of Binh Thanh District, as follows: 
- Current address: No. 71, Dien Bien Phu Street, Binh Thanh District, Ho Chi Minh City
- New address: No. 63A, Dien Bien Phu Street, Binh Thanh District, Ward 15, Binh Thanh District, Ho Chi Minh City
Yours faithfully,
